n <- 100; p <- 200
y <- rbinom(n=n,size=1,prob=0.5)
X <- lapply(1:2,function(x) matrix(rnorm(n*p),nrow=n,ncol=p))
reg <- palasso(y=y,X=X,family="binomial",trial=TRUE)
